• Atari Lynx
• Nintendo (NES)
• Super Nintendo (SNES)
• Game Boy (GB)
• Game Boy Color (GBC)
• Game Boy Advance (GBA)
• Sega Genesis (aka Megadrive)
• Sega Master System (SMS)
• Sega Game Gear (GG)
• Nintendo 64 (N64)
• PlayStation (PSX)
• PlayStation Portable (PSP)
• Nintendo DS (NDS)
• NEC PC Engine (PCE)
• Arcade (MAME2003, FBNeo)

• Automatically save and restore game states
• Quick save/load with slots
• Fastest emulation, therefore saves your battery to the MAX.
• Very high game compatibility. Run nearly all games without a problem.

• ROMs scanning and indexing
• Support for IPS/UPS zipped ROM patching.
• Optimized touch controls customization (size and position)
